Brightpoint completes acquisition . Brightpoint Inc said Wednesday it completed the previously announced acquisition of Brightpoint International Ltd . The 50 percent interest it acquired was owned by Technology Resources International Ltd . The purchase price included 400 , 000 shares of Brightpoint common stock plus $ 5 million in cash . John Maclean - Arnott , managing director of Brightpoint Europe , Middle East and Africa and Dana Marlin , marketing director of Brightpoint Asia Pacific , principal shareholders of Technology Resources , will continue in their capacities with Brightpoint International . Brightpoint International , based in Manchester , England , is responsible for all of Brightpoint Inc ' s sales and marketing efforts outside of North and South America . Brihgtpoint distributes wireless communication equipment . ( ( - - Chicago newsdesk 312 408 - 8787 ) ) 
